## v4.2.0 Release Notes (2025-07-09)

### New Features - User Configuration Directory
- **~/.claude-multiagent-pm/** - New user configuration directory structure
- **User-Defined Agents** - Custom agent system in ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/agents/user-defined/
- **Configuration Management** - YAML-based configuration in ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/config/
- **Template System** - Enhanced templates in ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/templates/
- **Training Modifications** - Agent training enhancements in ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/agents/training-modifications/

### Technical Enhancements
- **Directory Structure** - Migrated from ~/.claude-pm/ to ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/
- **Agent Architecture** - Enhanced user-defined agent loading system
- **Configuration Format** - YAML-based configuration for improved flexibility
- **Template Engine** - Advanced template system for rapid development
- **Documentation Updates** - Comprehensive documentation updates for v4.2.0

### Directory Features
- **User Directory** - ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/ for all user configurations
- **Agent Management** - Centralized agent definitions and custom agents
- **Configuration Hierarchy** - Structured configuration management
- **Template Library** - Comprehensive template system for projects and agents
